autoplay_lesson_will_start.description: Message when the lesson will start.

autoplay_up_next.description: Up next message in autoplay. Shown under next lesson title

connection_problem.description: Text that appears in training menu when there is a problem connecting to the training server

dialog_cancel_video_training.description: Button text for cancelling the dialog that takes the user to the video training web portal

dialog_content_autoplay_fail.description: Dialog text that appears when a training lesson is unavailable
dialog_content_autoplay_fail.message: The lesson you tried to access is unavailable. You can use the feedback link in the Training menu to report an error.

dialog_content_autoplay_login_fail.description: Dialog text that appears when user tries to play a training lesson from a shared link, and they are not logged in to their Google account
dialog_content_autoplay_login_fail.message: Please login to play shared lesson.

dialog_content_copy_link.message: The link has been copied to clipboard

dialog_content_end_lesson.description: Dialog text that appears when a user exits a training lesson in progress
dialog_content_end_lesson.message: This will end the lesson. Are you sure?

dialog_content_play_next_lesson.message: It looks like we are having some trouble playing the interactive version of this lesson, it has been reported to the training team. Please proceed to the next lesson.

dialog_content_play_video_lesson.message: It looks like we are having some trouble playing the interactive version of this lesson, you can load the video version to complete the lesson.

dialog_content_restart_lesson.description: Dialog text that appears when a user interrupts a training lesson and causes the current UI target of the lesson to no longer be visibile (e.g closing a menu). The dialog offers the user to restart the training lesson.
dialog_content_restart_lesson.message: We noticed that you interrupted the lesson, would you like to restart it? If you select No, then the lesson will end.

dialog_content_start_new_lesson.description: Dialog text that appears when a user tries to start a new training lessons while an existing training lesson is in progress
dialog_content_start_new_lesson.message: There is a lesson in progress. Starting a new lesson will end it. Do you want start the new lesson?

dialog_content_video_training.message: You will now be taken to a video training portal where G Suite training can be viewed. The video lessons are non-interactive, if you wish to access interactive lessons in your own G Suite then please switch to a supported language.

dialog_content_welcome.message: Would you like to learn how to use G Suite Training? Please adjust your volume as audio will be played.
